name: Colorness
description:
The first collector of this NFT will receive this original painting.
1st collector, please DM me via Twitter @Maks_Denysenko & I'll send it to you!

How I bought my own painting ☝️😃
⠀
That was a few years ago.
I had a great desire to do something pleasant for my surroundings.
⠀
The idea was as follows: 🌟
I take money for materials and create a picture, but for the work I do not take, charity in a word)
⠀
Eventually I got the money and asked for a long time what was expected of me 👌
⠀
When the work was done, I was told that the customer and the person to whom they planned to present this work did not understand each other correctly and this work does not suit her at all.
⠀
It was possible to give the job away, but I liked it so much ❤️ that I decided to return the money💎
⠀
I get high looking at her and I can communicate with the unconscious in a trance for a long time.

Artwork created by Maksym Denysenko in 2018, spray paint on canvas 90x90 cm, 8528x8582 pix
